        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "误区讲解",
          "block_bbox": [
            132,
            209,
            399,
            272
          ],
          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": 1
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "教室的面积一定，方砖的面积和所用砖的块数成反比例。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            136,
            315,
            607,
            509
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "用边长为15cm的方砖给教室铺地，需要2000块，如果改用边长为25cm的方砖铺地，需要多少块？（用比例知识解答）\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            141,
            543,
            609,
            872
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "错误解答：",
          "block_bbox": [
            145,
            904,
            329,
            945
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "解：设需要x块方砖。\n$\\begin{aligned}25x&=15\\times2000\\\\x&=1200\\end{aligned}$ ",
          "block_bbox": [
            145,
            979,
            513,
            1167
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "错因分析:这题用比例知识列的方程是错误的，本题成反比例的两个量不是方砖的边长和方砖的块数，而是方砖的面积和方砖的块数。",
          "block_bbox": [
            144,
            1202,
            617,
            1536
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "正确解答：",
          "block_bbox": [
            147,
            1570,
            329,
            1609
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "解：设需要x块方砖。\n\n$25^{2}x=15^{2}\\times2000$ \n\n$x=720$ \n\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            146,
            1640,
            516,
            1825
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 8
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "影1）",
          "block_bbox": [
            291,
            1861,
            476,
            1911
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 9
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "2.有一批书，这批书如果每包30本，要捆12包。如果每包20本，要捆多少包?\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            730,
            177,
            1855,
            327
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 10
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "3.装修一间客厅，用边长5dm的方砖铺地，需要80块，用边长4dm的方砖铺地，需要多少块？\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            722,
            727,
            1858,
            850
          ],
          "block_id": 11,
          "block_order": 11
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "4.制作一批零件，甲单独完成要6小时，已知甲、乙的工作效率比是3：2，那么乙单独完成要多长时间？\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            727,
            1252,
            1864,
            1369
          ],
          "block_id": 12,
          "block_order": 12
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
